cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks related to aerial images, such as semantic segmentation and geolocalization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of UAVs, which suggests the possibility of it being related to robotics (cs.RO). The use of deep neural networks and machine learning techniques indicates that it could also be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and graphics (cs.GR).
